headline: Secret Double Octopus Appoints Former NetApp CEO Dan Warmenhoven to its Board of Directors
summary: MENLO PARK, Calif., October 28, 2025--Secret Double Octopus, the leader in workforce authentication security, today announced the appointment of Dan Warmenhoven to its Board of Directors. Warmenhoven's extraordinary track record of scaling technology companies and deep cybersecurity experience will be invaluable as SDO scales to meet demand from heavily regulated global enterprises.
